URL = http://www.open-media.nl

=Description=

This Dutch Open Media foundation supports the 'open music' Simuze project in the Netherlands, related to the company Burobjorn (.nl).

"Simuze is a Dutch music community by and for music lovers and musicians.
Artists of all kinds can upload their own work(mp3) under a Creative
Commons license. Listeners can download the music for free and do
whatever they want with the music as long as this does not go against
the selected license."


